Cambodia 5 / 5
China 16 / 11
Egypt 4 / 2
Indonesia 29 / 22
Iraq 2 / 2
Thailand 22 / 14
Turkey 12 / 4
Viet Nam 93 / 42
Total 190 / 107
The total number of cases includes the number of deaths. WHO reports only
laboratory-confirmed cases. - Mod.RY]
